[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1357","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1357.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1143","title":"SGI IRIX runtime linker 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.x 及更早版本中的运行时链接器程序 rld 存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过利用 setuid 和 setgid 程序在链接过程中对 rld 进行操纵，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞源于 rld 在处理特权程序时未正确验证调用者身份，导致低权限用户可借助已授权的 setuid/setgid 二进制文件执行任意代码，实现完全控制目标系统。攻击者需拥有本地 shell 访问权限，无需其他认证条件，攻击复杂度较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1143"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:48.800","remediation":"立即应用 SGI 安全公告 19970504-01-PX 中提供的 rld 补丁，升级 IRIX 到包含修复的最新版本。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统；若无法迁移，应限制本地用户对 setuid/setgid 程序的访问权限，并监控 rld 的异常调用行为作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/h-65.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2109","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1143.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1143","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1143.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1143.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-rf38-8rrc-q77r/GHSA-rf38-8rrc-q77r.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88532/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1143.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000175.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--308298c9-890d-401d-a3c9-50285f139b1f.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1357.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0163","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0163.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0064","title":"IBM AIX lquerylv 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统的 lquerylv 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地低权限用户可通过向该程序发送精心构造的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 AIX 多个版本，需要本地用户身份才能利用，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0064"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.583","remediation":"立即安装 IBM AIX APAR IX73924 安全补丁，或升级至 AIX 4.2.1 及以上版本。若无法立即打补丁，可执行 `chmod u-s /usr/sbin/lquerylv` 移除该程序的 setuid 位，以阻止本地普通用户通过此漏洞获取 root 权限；同时限制不可信用户的本地访问权限作为深度防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418428&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/335","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0064","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0064.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0064.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mqqq-75g7-35v7/GHSA-mqqq-75g7-35v7.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0163.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0096","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0036","title":"SGI IRIX login 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.4 及之前版本中的 /bin/login 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞。当 LOCKOUT 参数设置为非零值时，攻击者可通过精心构造的输入触发缓冲区溢出，以 root 权限创建或破坏系统文件，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，利用门槛较低，危害严重。SGI 已发布安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":8.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0036"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.110","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 1997 年 5 月安全公告 19970508-02-PX 提供的修补补丁。临时缓解措施：在 /etc/default/login 配置文件中将 LOCKOUT 参数设为 0 并重启 login 服务。由于 SGI IRIX 已停止技术支持多年，建议尽快迁移至仍受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-106.shtml","http://www.osvdb.org/990","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/557","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/cisagov/vulnrichment/blob/f47735aa52980ccd9473eed79b62a27c199a2cfa/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/SSVC/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0036","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/dcc6735c9c3e50e93de820fa1ac9c54ecf6b2577/1999/CVE-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0036.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-00xx/CVE-1999-0036.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0444","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0259","title":"cfingerd 用户信息泄露漏洞","description":"cfingerd 是一款可配置的 finger 服务守护程序，由于其未对用户查询进行充分的访问控制过滤，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 `search.**@target` 查询请求，枚举系统上所有已注册用户账号信息，造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响使用 cfingerd 的 Unix/Linux 系统，攻击者可在未授权条件下远程利用，为进一步的社会工程学攻击或密码爆破提供用户列表基础。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0259"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:01.240","remediation":"升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.3 或更高版本以修复用户列表泄露漏洞；如无法升级，建议在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 finger 服务（注释掉 finger 行），或使用 tcpwrappers（hosts.allow/hosts.deny）限制可访问源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0259.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0259","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0259.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/322.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/finger.rules","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96/GHSA-m4g2-9rpr-wc96.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cfinger_search.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0444.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0101","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0037","title":"FreeBSD Metamail 任意命令执行漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 系统自带的 metamail 邮件处理工具存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的 MIME 邮件消息，在消息头中嵌入恶意命令。当用户使用 metamail 处理该恶意邮件时，漏洞被触发，导致以当前用户权限在系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，但需要用户主动触发邮件处理操作，影响范围较广。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0037"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:25.340","remediation":"升级 metamail 至已过滤 MIME 邮件头 shell 元字符的修补版本；若无法升级，建议直接卸载 metamail（pkg delete metamail）并改用 procmail 或 maildrop 等现代邮件处理工具替代；同时配置邮件客户端不自动调用 metamail 处理来自不可信来源的 MIME 邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0037"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1191","title":"Sun Solaris chkey 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 及之前版本中的 chkey 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地用户通过向该命令传递超长命令行参数，可触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取 root 权限。攻击者无需任何系统权限即可利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1191"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-05-19","updated":"2024-06-16","remediation":"应用 Sun 安全公告 144 中提供的补丁，升级 Solaris 系统至已修复版本，或限制 chkey 命令的 setuid 权限以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2024-06-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418335&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/144","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/207","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7442.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1264","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1264.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1402","title":"Sun Solaris FreeBSD UNIX 域套接字访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.x、SunOS 4.x 以及 4.4 版本之前的 BSD 类操作系统存在 UNIX 域套接字访问控制绕过漏洞。系统内核在创建 UNIX 域套接字时未正确强制执行文件权限检查，导致套接字的访问权限设置被完全忽略。本地非授权用户可直接连接到这些套接字并向其写入数据，从而干扰或控制使用该套接字的应用程序，进而造成服务中断、数据篡改或权限提升等后果。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1402"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:21.837","remediation":"建议将 Solaris 升级至已修复该问题的补丁集群版本（Solaris 2.6 安装 Sun 官方内核补丁后版本），BSD 系统升级至 4.4 或相应发行版修复版本（如 FreeBSD 3.2+）。在无法立即升级时，可改用 TCP 回路地址套接字或调整相关守护进程的数据目录权限为 0700 并归属专用用户，以限制本地非授权用户连接域套接字。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167418317&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602248718482&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7172.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/456","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19346"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1264.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1418","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1418.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1232","title":"SGI IRIX day5datacopier 不可信搜索路径漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 系统中的 day5datacopier 工具存在不可信搜索路径漏洞。本地攻击者可通过修改 PATH 环境变量，使其指向恶意的 cp 程序，当 day5datacopier 被触发执行时，系统将加载攻击者预设的恶意程序而非系统原生的 cp 命令，从而导致任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.2 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1232"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.997","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.3 或更高版本，或在 day5datacopier 脚本中使用 cp 命令的绝对路径 /bin/cp 替代相对路径 cp，同时限制普通用户对关键脚本的写权限并移除当前目录（.）从 PATH 环境变量中。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420994&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/8559","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3316"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1418.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1355","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1355.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1141","title":"Ascom Timeplex 路由器调试模式信息泄露漏洞","description":"Ascom Timeplex 路由器存在调试模式信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，仅通过发送特定序列的 CTRL-D 控制字符即可使目标路由器进入调试模式，从而获取敏感配置信息或执行未授权操作。该漏洞影响 Ascom Timeplex 系列路由器，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1141"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:48.530","remediation":"此漏洞影响已停止支持的旧版 Ascom Timeplex 路由器。建议立即更换为受支持的现代路由器设备；如无法更换，应严格限制管理接口的网络访问（仅允许受信任 IP 通过专用管理 VLAN 访问），在边界防火墙上封锁路由器管理端口（如 Telnet 23/UDP 161 SNMP），并禁用不必要的远程管理服务以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420981&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1824","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1141.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1141","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1141.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1141.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m26q-6j78-pcw5/GHSA-m26q-6j78-pcw5.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88528/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1141.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--b1589dcb-a487-4cbe-ad69-2015283a27d6.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1355.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1184","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9155,\"outputTokens\":25,\"totalTokens\":10844}}","description":"Elm 邮件客户端 2.4 及更早版本（含 2.3）在处理环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序在读取 TERM 环境变量时未对输入长度进行边界校验，本地用户可通过在 shell 中设置超长的 TERM 环境变量后启动 Elm，使恶意构造的数据覆盖栈上返回地址，从而以 Elm 进程权限（通常为目标用户权限）执行任意代码并提升本地权限。该漏洞影响采用受影响版本 Elm 的本地系统用户，攻击前提是攻击者已拥有目标系统的本地登录权限，利用方式简单，仅需设置环境变量即可触发，CVSS 基础评分约为 4.6，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1184"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.890","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Elm 2.5 或更高版本（该版本已修复 TERM 环境变量缓冲区溢出）。如无法立即升级，可在 /etc/profile 或用户 shell 配置中对 TERM 变量长度做限制（如 truncate 至 40 字符以内），并避免以特权用户运行 elm；临时缓解可在 setuid 环境中用 env -u TERM 方式启动，移除 TERM 变量传入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420967&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420970&w=2","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/22836","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d69ab21f83909859ed75ab8ba3287f9f633b856f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1184.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1184","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1184.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c9ec7f26a52f816468b636e23146049097db5070/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1184.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7jcx-v99p-6xwr/GHSA-7jcx-v99p-6xwr.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83053/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1184.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000167.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1246","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1246.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1158","title":"Sun Solaris PAM 模块缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 操作系统的可插拔认证模块（PAM）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当用户通过 passwd、yppasswd、nispasswd 等程序修改密码时，会调用存在缺陷的 PAM 模块进行认证处理，由于对输入数据长度缺乏充分校验，本地攻击者可构造特制的认证请求触发缓冲区溢出，从而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1 等多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。官方建议安装 Sun 提供的安全补丁或升级系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1158"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.657","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至 2.6 及以上版本，该版本已修复 PAM 模块和 unix_scheme 的缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可限制本地用户对 passwd/yppasswd/nispasswd 的 SUID 执行权限（chmod 4750 /bin/passwd），并安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 103670-03（SPARC）或 103671-03（x86）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/139&type=0&nav=sec.sba","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/341","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1158.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1158","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1158.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1158.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-m3h3-j5g8-pq9j/GHSA-m3h3-j5g8-pq9j.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83036/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000166.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1158.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1246.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1246.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1246.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1454","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1454.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1286","title":"SGI IRIX addnetpr 本地符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.2 及更早版本中的 addnetpr 工具（/usr/lib/netaddpr）存在本地权限提升漏洞。该程序在处理临时文件时未正确检查符号链接，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接指向任意系统文件，诱导程序以高权限覆写目标文件，从而修改关键系统配置或二进制文件，最终获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.2 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用前提是攻击者拥有本地账户。，最终获取 root 权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1286"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-05-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:06.797","remediation":"该漏洞存在于已停止维护的 SGI IRIX 6.2 及更早版本中，厂商已不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级至受支持的现代操作系统（如 Linux 或 BSD 系列），彻底弃用 SGI IRIX 系统。如无法立即迁移，应移除 /usr/lib/addnetpr 的 SUID 权限（chmod 0755 /usr/lib/addnetpr），并限制可执行该程序的用户组范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420927&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/8560","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/330","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1433","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1286.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1286","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1286.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1286.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-x5rx-8ccg-vqfm/GHSA-x5rx-8ccg-vqfm.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1286.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000164.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ef0f8546-b376-4711-8b28-ce33c3173199.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1454.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1267","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1410","title":"SGI IRIX addnetpr 本地符号链接任意文件写入权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 5.3 与 6.2 系统中的 addnetpr（/usr/lib/netaddpr）工具在处理打印机临时文件时存在符号链接漏洞。由于该程序以 root 权限运行且未对临时文件路径进行安全校验，本地低权限用户可预先创建指向任意系统文件的符号链接，诱导 addnetpr 以 root 身份覆盖该文件内容。攻击者借此可覆写如 /etc/passwd 等关键文件，进而实现本地权限提升、获取 root 权限。该漏洞仅影响本地已登录的普通用户，需具备执行 addnetpr 的权限且系统运行上述受影响版本，利用门槛较低但危害明显。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1410"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:22.870","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至已修复该问题的补丁版本（IRIX 6.2 建议应用 0419 或 0434 补丁集，IRIX 5.3 应用对应补丁）；在无法立即打补丁时，临时将 /usr/lib/netaddpr 移除 setuid 位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/lib/netaddpr）并限制普通用户对打印临时目录的写权限，以缓解符号链接攻击导致的任意文件写入与提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420927&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/330","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19260","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1410.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1410","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1410.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1410.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-c246-pm63-mr5c/GHSA-c246-pm63-mr5c.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/330/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--64c39b8b-8e89-49b1-a933-cbeea4370b60.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1410.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1267.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1267.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1278","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1278.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1461","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9190,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10874}}","description":"SGI IRIX 5.3 至 6.5.10 系统中，InPerson 套件的 inpview 程序在启动时会直接信任 PATH 环境变量来查找并执行 ttsession 程序，而未对其进行安全校验。本地已登录的低权限用户可通过在 PATH 中前置一个伪装的恶意 ttsession 程序（特洛伊木马）来诱使 inpview 以 root 权限执行该恶意程序，从而完成本地权限提升、获取 root 访问权限。该漏洞影响上述多个 IRIX 版本，攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地系统账户且可修改自身环境变量，利用方式即构造恶意 PATH 指向伪造的 ttsession 程序。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1461"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:29.400","remediation":"升级到 SGI IRIX 6.5.11 或更高版本（已修复 inpview 对 PATH 的信任问题）。如暂时无法升级，可移除 inpview 的 setuid root 位（执行 chmod u-s /usr/IP32/bin/inpview 或对应路径），并限制普通用户对 InPerson 套件的访问权限；同时清理不可信用户可写目录、避免将其加入 PATH，以阻止构造伪造 ttsession 实现本地提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420921&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/381","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19304","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1461.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1461","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1461.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1461.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-49q4-89v2-j76r/GHSA-49q4-89v2-j76r.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1461.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000163.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ee8d9334-cb20-4047-bf95-2d29463c817e.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1278.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1316","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1316.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1067","title":"SGI MachineInfo CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"SGI MachineInfo CGI 程序默认安装在部分 SGI IRIX Web 服务器上，该程序未对访问权限进行限制，导致远程攻击者可直接通过 HTTP 请求获取目标主机的系统状态信息，包括进程列表、网络连接、系统负载等敏感数据，从而为后续渗透攻击提供情报支撑。该漏洞攻击门槛低，仅需网络可达即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1067"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-05-07","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"删除或重命名 SGI Web 服务器上的 MachineInfo CGI 脚本（通常位于 /cgi-bin/machineinfo），或通过 Web 服务器配置限制仅允许可信任 IP 访问；升级 SGI IRIX 操作系统至 6.5 以上版本以移除默认安装的该 CGI 程序；如业务不需要此功能，直接移除该脚本文件以彻底消除信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420919&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1316.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1316.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1316.toml"}]